org.cougaar.core.qos.metrics
Class DeltaValueQualifier

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.core.qos.metrics.DeltaValueQualifier
All Implemented Interfaces:
Constants, MetricNotificationQualifier
public class DeltaValueQualifier
extends java.lang.Object
implements MetricNotificationQualifier, Constants

Instances of this class can be used to restrict callbacks from MetricsService subscriptions unless the new value differs from the previous value by a given delta. These qualifiers are stateful and therefore cannot be shared across multiple subscriptions.

See Also:
CredibilityQualifier
